---
// PostHog (US Cloud).
//
// Autocapture + automatic $pageview are on by default. Anonymous visits
// stay anonymous (`person_profiles: 'identified_only'`) since we don't
// call identify() anywhere — keeps person-profile quota for actual sign-ups
// if/when we ever add them.
//
// Storage falls back to localStorage rather than cookies (PostHog default),
// so this stays out of the cookie-banner regulatory perimeter for first-
// party analytics. Update before adding any cross-site / advertising use.
//
// Included from <Base> (covers index, 404, /dev/glass-tuner) and from the
// stand-alone calendar shell (`pages/calendar.astro`). The /dev/ guard at
// the bottom of the snippet skips init on internal dev tools.
